text: India has participated at the 2019 Summer Universiade in Naples, Italy. Dutee Chand became the first Indian women sprinter to win gold at the World Universiade championship, clocking 11.32 seconds in the 100m race. ==References== 2019 Category:Nations at the 2019 Summer Universiade Category:2019 in Indian sport
title: India at the 2019 Summer Universiade
